            <p class="prose">DCA smooths the worst-timing risk because most of the dollars get deployed at prices other than the peak. The question is whether the resulting positions, measured by total wealth accumulated, favor bitcoin or the conventional comparators. The answer in the historical record &mdash; for every anchor date the page tests &mdash; is bitcoin.</p>

